            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "邱士縉Stanley 4月開show做行走荷爾蒙 將離港拍戲女友信任唔Check行蹤",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"邱士縉Stanley 4月開show做行走荷爾蒙 將離港拍戲女友信任唔Check行蹤\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/92ac798f7f3f88c7ec246e7bab5a3571/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250313/_2025031321165839208.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">邱士縉Stanley 4月開show做行走荷爾蒙 將離港拍戲女友信任唔Check行蹤</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>MIRROR成員邱士縉（Stanley）現身尖沙咀出席護膚品牌活動，他最近在馬來西亞拍戲，回港出席是次活動後，再返馬來西亞繼續拍攝至月底，指並非動作片所以不太辛苦，但天氣較潮濕，又會突然下雨，拍外景又不時遇上當地唸經儀式，要稍停拍攝。\n\n</p><h2>行走荷爾蒙</h2>\n<p>Stanley大讚當地美食又平又美味，他4月要與小組成員Ian、Jer和Tiger舉行演唱會，所以飲食要節制，每日也去跑步一小時。談到女友Alina社交網留言「到處都是線眼」，他笑言因為當地四處「阿蓮榴槤」、「阿蓮水餃」，因此而開玩笑，又稱拍拖多年女友已很放心，豎起尾巴已知道想怎樣，女友不會查他的行蹤，他也不會四處去玩。Stanley忙於拍戲，Ian又赴英國巡唱，是否沒時間排練小組的演唱會？他說現時先練習自己部份，亦有夾band及跳舞環節，稍後齊人仍有時間排練。問他是否演唱會的肌肉擔當？他說電影角色不能太大隻，要在演員、歌手之間協調和拉扯。談到演唱會主題「Wild &amp; Gentle」，他表示展現男性性感，Ian有內歛的性感，Tiger有狂野性感，Jer有rock的性感，而他則是sexy的性感，是行走荷爾蒙。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4135805/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"Stanley話演唱會主題「Wild &amp; Gentle」，將會展現男性性感。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ababdeef9ecdda461c743c8b38c8a6eb/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-13_at_13_55_48_2_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Stanley話演唱會主題「Wild &amp; Gentle」，將會展現男性性感。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4135806/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"Stanley4月show炫耀肌肉。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7533308045537e8d01960b79e6c97a0d/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-13_at_13_55_48.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Stanley4月show炫耀肌肉。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4135918/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"Stanley與Alina拍拖多年。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e5bfe932403a205e28b42ff84e2d3b1d/2025-03/130A4756.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Stanley與Alina拍拖多年。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4135919/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"Stanley、Alina十分信任對方。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9b6bd6afc5216ee5a1fbf98176510a3f/2025-03/FJRr_qg7O2QdPsbZTdigf0tEZA74sIr3l3ihg5d4oYM.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Stanley、Alina十分信任對方。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4135936/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"最近姜濤（左）拍團綜驚青燒棉花糖被花姐呼喝唔夠man，Stanley指姜濤為「姜Man」，會越來越man。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/43e06e78ca356d29ca721fa006ef81c4/2025-03/0F0A3942.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        最近姜濤（左）拍團綜驚青燒棉花糖被花姐呼喝唔夠man，Stanley指姜濤為「姜Man」，會越來越man。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4135937/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"Stanley預告4月show會炫耀肌肉。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8084d7bd4d6e06b6c3abb265ef2f3501/2025-03/183654674_2884538158474040_1403313819221997565_n.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Stanley預告4月show會炫耀肌肉。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4135807/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"Stanley在活動上派心，fans尖叫受落。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ebb4fbedaeb25f4c4a95b5885d5c3adf/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-13_at_13_55_50_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Stanley在活動上派心，fans尖叫受落。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4135814/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"Stanley fans舉牌應援。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6c88cbc8b881376d9e2b3ef9d6d66ed7/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-13_at_13_55_44_0.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Stanley fans舉牌應援。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4135815/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"Stanley與衛詩雅一身雪白打扮出席活動。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/858c7365bef4e79e491901062186a1a0/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-13_at_13_55_45_3__0.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Stanley與衛詩雅一身雪白打扮出席活動。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4135816/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"品牌高層同Stanley自拍。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ec64dccef0f82262f3d50b182884ae7f/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-13_at_13_55_46_1__0.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        品牌高層同Stanley自拍。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>每個小組也會拍團綜</h2>\n<p>談到MIRROR「妹豬組」成員赴韓國拍團綜，Stanley透露應該每個小組也會拍團綜，其小組會在年中後拍攝，他想去歐洲歎世界。問到姜濤拍團綜驚青燒棉花糖被花姐呼喝做事要man一點，姜糖指花姐沒安全意識，Stanley表示沒看片段，相信花姐比姜濤更擔心，更會衡量安全性，花姐叫姜濤man是出於像媽媽般提醒姜濤要大個仔，不要像小朋友要人照顧。問他會否教姜濤做個man男人？他指姜濤已被稱為「姜Man」，會越來越man。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
